<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Pages on 𝄇|Hentilix's Blog</title><link>https://hentilix.pages.dev/page/</link><description>Recent content in Pages on 𝄇|Hentilix's Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><atom:link href="https://hentilix.pages.dev/page/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title/><link>https://hentilix.pages.dev/page/thoughts/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hentilix.pages.dev/page/thoughts/</guid><description/></item><item><title>About Me</title><link>https://hentilix.pages.dev/page/about/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hentilix.pages.dev/page/about/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;NEUCS大一新生，梦想是去鹰角上班，曾经很喜欢明日方舟，现已淡坑。最喜欢的游戏是博德之门3、杀戮尖塔和素晴日。喜欢玩Galgame但不喜欢废萌。杂食听众，古典、爵士、金属、摇滚、电子、说唱、流行、实验、民乐，来者不拒。Hi-Fi发烧友，设备是Sennheiser HD600 + Fosi Audio SK07。羽毛球爱好者，半个童子功。会黑管和围棋。热爱阅读与写作，最喜欢的作家是陀思妥耶夫斯基和加缪，最近在读E.M.齐奥朗。对吃很有一套，热爱美食😋。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Message Board</title><link>https://hentilix.pages.dev/page/message/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hentilix.pages.dev/page/message/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;欢迎留言 ！&lt;/p&gt;
